summary: Do you ever think of all the scenes from iron man 2 that were deleted, scenes that made it clear to a casual viewer how suicidal...
body: Do you ever think of all the scenes from iron man 2 that were deleted, scenes that made it clear to a casual viewer how suicidal tony was, how much he was spiraling and how all of his “egotistical” outbursts were just him trying to use up the rest of his time as entertaining as possible bc I do and I hate that we were robbed of those scenes on screen
